# Vercel serves the repo root as static files. Deny everything by default and
# re-include only the public marketing site, so internal brain notes, prospect
# data, client files/invoices, automation source and strategy docs are never
# published to the web.
/*

# Public pages and config
!index.html
!automations.html
!automation-journey.html
!websites.html
!robots.txt
!sitemap.xml
!vercel.json

# Public assets referenced by the site
!assets
!brand
!downloads
!one-pagers
!videos
!og
!Logo
!Brand_Assets
